Subject: [PATCH] Fix compile errors on Linux 6.12

Upstream commit fe73965d0786 ("HID: change return type of report_fixup()
to const") changed the return value of the report_fixup callback.

Also, unaligned.h was moved from asm to linux.

Fix both issues on kernels >= 6.12.
